summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Lighting Department and accepting a franchise from the Washington State Highway Commission (Franchise No. 5841) for the construction, operation and maintenance of an underground 115 KV transmission line on a portion of State Route 5 in Sections 5 and 8, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M. between East 43rd Street and East 75th Street; Seattle, King County, Washington.
